OL,3,CWater companies to invest more than
OL,4,C#180m to tackle sewage spills
OL,6,FThe investment will support the effort
OL,7,Fto roll out storm overflow prevention
OL,8,Fmeasures by April 2025, ITV News'
OL,9,FAisha Zahid reports
OL,11,FWater companies are to invest more
OL,12,Fthan #180m to tackle sewage spills as
OL,13,Fpart of a fast-tracked investment in
OL,14,Foverflow prevention measures by April
OL,15,F2025.
OL,17,FThe investment includes artificial
OL,18,Fintelligence systems, accelerated
OL,19,Fwetland programmes, installing new in-
OL,20,Fsewer monitors and recruiting and
OL,21,Ftraining specialist staff.
