OL,3,CWater companies to invest more than
OL,4,C#180m to tackle sewage spills
OL,6,FThe government said it expects the
OL,7,Fmeasures to prevent more than 8,000
OL,8,Fspills polluting English waterways.
OL,10,FAnglian Water will invest #50 million,
OL,11,FSevern Trent will invest #41 million,
OL,12,FSouthern will invest #10 million,
OL,13,FSouth West will invest #32 million,
OL,14,FUnited Utilities will invest #39
OL,15,Fmillion and Wessex will invest #8
OL,16,Fmillion.
