OL,3,CWater companies to invest more than
OL,4,C#180m to tackle sewage spills
OL,6,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Barclay
OL,7,Fsaid the investment is part of
OL,8,Fgovernment efforts to "push for better
OL,9,Fperformance from water companies and
OL,10,Fhold them to account".
OL,12,FHe said: "The amount of sewage being
OL,13,Fspilled into our rivers is completely
OL,14,Funacceptable and the public rightly
OL,15,Fexpects action.
OL,17,F"This money will mean more cutting-
OL,18,Fedge technology, including artificial
OL,19,Fintelligence, and more specialist
OL,20,Fstaff to detect and reduce spills.
