OL,3,CWater companies to invest more than
OL,4,C#180m to tackle sewage spills
OL,6,FIt is the latest move to tackle
OL,7,Fconcerns over levels of pollution
OL,8,Fbeing dumped into rivers, lakes and
OL,9,Faround the coasts from sources
OL,10,Fincluding overflow pipes and
OL,11,Fprocessing plants, causing harm to
OL,12,Fwildlife and the health of beachgoers
OL,13,Fas well as affecting tourism and
OL,14,Fleisure industries.
OL,16,FGiles Bristow, chief executive of
OL,17,FSurfers Against Sewage, said: "It's
OL,18,Fgreat to see the Government fast-
OL,19,Ftracking investment on the decades-old
OL,20,Fissue of sewage pollution.
