OL,3,CWater companies to invest more than
OL,4,C#180m to tackle sewage spills
OL,6,F"The informed and angry voices of
OL,7,Fconstituents across the UK are clearly
OL,8,Fmaking those in power listen and take
OL,9,Fvisible actions to address the sewage
OL,10,Fscandal.
OL,12,F"Despite today's welcome announcement,
OL,13,Fquestions still remain on the scale
OL,14,Fand scope of the Government's
OL,15,Fambitions for our rivers and seas.
OL,17,F"We'll be watching closely to ensure
OL,18,Fthat it's the polluters, not the
OL,19,Fconsumer, that pays to clean up this
OL,20,Fmess."
